Install Bootstrap in Angular with scss

Uninstalling the Angular CLI
npm uninstall -g @angular/cli

Clear the cache
npm cache clean --force

install angular
npm install -g @angular/cli@latest
npm i -g @angular/cli@13.0.0

Create workspace:
ng new [PROJECT NAME]

enter to proyect(very important!!!!!)
cd [PROJECT NAME]

install bootstrap
$ npm install bootstrap --save

import bootstrap in styles.scss:
@import '~bootstrap/scss/bootstrap';
or
@import "~bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css";
or add  in angular.json:
"styles": [
              "src/styles.css",
              "node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
            ],
            "scripts": [
              "node_modules/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
            ]


in app.component.html add:
<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Button</button>

Run the application:
ng serve

desinstalar e instalar toastr
npm uninstall ngx-toastr@
npm install ngx-toastr@13.0.0 --save
npm install @angular/ animations --save
